---
---

<section id="beta" class="beta-cta">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="inner">
      <span class="hero-emoji" aria-hidden="true">🌸</span>
      <h2>Prêt à cataloguer vos fleurs ?</h2>
      <p>Rejoignez la bêta et soyez parmi les premiers à essayer FloraPin.</p>

      <!--
        Remplacez l'attribut action par votre URL Formspree :
        https://formspree.io/f/<VOTRE_ID>
        Ou pointez vers un endpoint backend dédié.
      -->
      <form
        class="form"
        action="https://formspree.io/f/VOTRE_ID"
        method="POST"
        novalidate
      >
        <div class="form-row">
          <label for="beta-email" class="sr-only">Adresse e-mail</label>
          <input
            id="beta-email"
            type="email"
            name="email"
            placeholder="votre@email.com"
            required
            autocomplete="email"
          />
          <button type="submit">Je veux tester FloraPin →</button>
        </div>
        <p class="legal">
          Votre adresse e-mail sera utilisée uniquement pour la bêta FloraPin.
          <a href="/politique-de-confidentialite">Politique de confidentialité</a>.
        </p>
      </form>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .beta-cta {
    padding: var(--section-py) 0;
    background: linear-gradient(140deg, var(--green-50) 0%, #fff3fa 100%);
  }

  .inner {
    text-align: center;
    max-width: 560px;
    margin: 0 auto;
  }

  .hero-emoji {
    font-size: 3.2rem;
    display: block;
    margin-bottom: 20px;
    line-height: 1;
  }

  h2 {
    font-size: clamp(1.6rem, 3vw, 2.4rem);
    font-weight: 700;
    color: var(--green-900);
    margin-bottom: 12px;
  }

  p {
    font-size: 1rem;
    color: var(--gray-600);
    margin-bottom: 32px;
  }

  .form-row {
    display: flex;
    border-radius: 14px;
    overflow: hidden;
    box-shadow: 0 4px 24px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
    margin-bottom: 12px;
  }

  input[type="email"] {
    flex: 1;
    padding: 16px 20px;
    font-family: var(--font);
    font-size: 1rem;
    border: none;
    outline: none;
    background: var(--white);
    color: var(--gray-900);
    min-width: 0;
  }

  input[type="email"]::placeholder { color: #9ca3af; }

  button[type="submit"] {
    background: var(--green-700);
    color: var(--white);
    font-family: var(--font);
    font-size: 0.88rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    padding: 16px 22px;
    border: none;
    cursor: pointer;
    white-space: nowrap;
    transition: background 0.2s;
  }

  button[type="submit"]:hover { background: var(--green-800); }

  .legal {
    font-size: 0.76rem;
    color: #9ca3af;
    margin-bottom: 0;
  }

  .legal a {
    color: var(--green-700);
    text-decoration: underline;
  }

  /* Accessibilité */
  .sr-only {
    position: absolute;
    width: 1px;
    height: 1px;
    padding: 0;
    margin: -1px;
    overflow: hidden;
    clip: rect(0, 0, 0, 0);
    white-space: nowrap;
    border-width: 0;
  }

  @media (max-width: 500px) {
    .form-row { flex-direction: column; }

    button[type="submit"] {
      border-radius: 0;
      padding: 16px;
    }
  }
</style>
